5
[p 
	"With the addition of three new shortcuts, Sonic and Tails finish the game about 45 seconds faster than the 
	[a class=intlink href=/1935S 
		"previous run
	]a
	". Although neither Nitsuja nor Upthorn were actively involved in this improvement, they are listed as co-authors because their input comprises over 90% of the movie.
	$LF
]p
